{"word":"G1920 - ἐπιγίνομαι - epigínomai - ep-ig-in'-om-ahee - Blow","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιγίνομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epigínomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ig-in'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Blow</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நடைபெறு"},{"paragraph":"1. to become or happen afterward; to be born after"},{"paragraph":"2. to come to, arrive"},{"paragraph":"3. to arise, spring up, come on"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G1096 - γίνομαι - gínomai - ghin'-om-ahee/1096\">G1096</a>; to <i>arrive upon</i>, that is, <i>spring up</i> (as a wind): - blow.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}